snippet.title: Johnny Depp And Amber Heard PETITIONS Reaching MASSIVE NUMBERS! - Does It Matter Though?
snippet.description:
The petitions to bring Johnny Depp back as Grindelwald, Jack Sparrow and to fire Amber Heard from Aquaman 2 have reach insane numbers in just a few days. Which is fantastic. But will these petitions actually do anything? Sadly no. Let's discuss! Let me know what you think and make sure to subscribe to the channel for more content!!
